        {
            "title": "黑期跌88點   ADR低水133點  信義光能低水7.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期跌88點或0.34%，報25539。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恒指昨天收市低水133點或0.52%，報25533點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：信義光能官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">主要ADR幾全線報跌，信義光能(00968) ADR折合港元計收報3.01元，較香港收市價大幅低水7.9% ; 新東方(09901) ADR折合港元計收報3.01元，較香港收市價大幅低水3.8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">理想汽車(02015) ADR折合港元計收報116.15元，較香港收市價低2.2% ; 比亞迪(01211) ADR較香港收市價低水1.1%，折合130.64港元</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988) ADR折合港元計收報118.88元，較香港收市價低1.2% ; 美團(03690) ADR較香港收市價低0.8%，折合133.34港元 ;騰訊(00700) ADR折合港元計收報552.67元，較香港收市價高0.8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報102.02元，較香港收市價低0.2% ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣70.99元，較香港收市價低水0.4% ;港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣445.9元，較香港收市價低0.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">僅中通快遞(02057)ADR高水，折合港幣158.89元，較香港收市價高水0.4%。攜程(09961)ADR折合港幣506.66元，平水。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報25505點，跌178點，較昨日恒指收市25667點，低水162點，成交12386張。國指夜市期指收報9194點，較昨日國指收市低水64點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15120290-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e8%b7%8c88%e9%bb%9e-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4133%e9%bb%9e-%e4%bf%a1%e7%be%a9%e5%85%89%e8%83%bd%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b47-9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-25 08:55:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
