        {
            "title": "中石化上半年油氣當量產量按年升2% 天然氣產量增5.1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國石化(00386)公布上半年生產經營數據，其中油氣當量量達2.63億桶油當量，按年提升2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國石化微博\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_source-web_中國石化2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國石化微博\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_source-web_中國石化2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國石化微博</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內天然氣產量則達7362.8億立方英尺，去年同期增加5.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">原油加工量1.2億噸，則較去年同期減少5.3%。乙烯產量756.3萬噸，按年增長16.4%。境內成品油總經銷量8705萬噸，按年減少3.4%；其中零售為5453萬噸，按年跌4.3%，直銷及分銷為3252萬噸，按年減2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15119057-%e4%b8%ad%e7%9f%b3%e5%8c%96%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e6%b2%b9%e6%b0%a3%e7%95%b6%e9%87%8f%e7%94%a2%e9%87%8f%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%872-%e5%a4%a9%e7%84%b6%e6%b0%a3%e7%94%a2%e9%87%8f%e5%a2%9e5-1",
